ut%3F%20It%20was%20on%20the%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cstrange%20decision%E2%80%9D%20to%20allow%20the%20murder%20accused%20to%20intervene%20in%20his%20writ%20petition%2C%20something%20that%20is%20legally%20untenable.%20Sandeep%E2%80%99s%20writ%20petition%20was%20filed%20challenging%20the%20session%E2%80%99s%20court%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20accept%20a%20closure%20report%20filed%20by%20the%20CBI%20on%20April%2013%2C%202018%2C%20claiming%20that%2C%20%E2%80%9Cno%20further%20prosecutable%20evidence%20emerged%20against%20any%20person%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20murder%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESandeep%20had%20named%20Virendra%20Mhaiskar%2C%20chairman%20and%20managing%20director%2C%20Ideal%20Road%20Builder%20(IRB)%2C%20as%20one%20of%20the%20prime%20accused%20in%20the%20case.%20The%20then%20division%20bench%20of%20the%20Bombay%20high%20court%20comprising%20Justice%20Ranjit%20More%20and%20Justice%20Bharati%20Dangre%20had%2C%20however%2C%20allowed%20Mhaiskar%20to%20intervene%20in%20the%20matter%2C%20though%20he%20was%20not%20even%20made%20a%20party.%20Against%20this%20order%2C%20Sandeep%20filed%20a%20Special%20Leave%20Petition%20(SLP)%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20Strangely%20the%20CBI%2C%20which%20was%20made%20a%20party%20in%20the%20petition%2C%20had%20not%20appeared%20before%20the%20high%20court.%20Sandeep%20points%20out%20that%20each%20time%20he%20has%20approached%20the%20court%2C%20instead%20of%20the%20CBI%2C%20it%20was%20Mhaiskar%20who%20would%20intervene.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20division%20bench%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20judges%20Justices%20Abhay%20Oka%20and%20Panjak%20Mittal%20observed%3A%20%E2%80%9CMuch%20is%20said%20by%20the%20learned%20senior%20counsel%20appearing%20for%20the%20appellant%20about%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20Writ%20Petitions%20were%20taken%20up%20and%20decided%20by%20the%20High%20Court.%E2%80%9D%20The%20bench%20further%20directed%20the%20high%20court%20to%20%E2%80%9Creconsider%20the%20Writ%20Petitions%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CAccordingly%2C%20we%20set%20aside%20the%20impugned%20order%20dated%2018th%20March%2C%202019%20in%20Writ%20Petition%20Nos.639%20of%202019%20and%203191%20of%202016%20and%20restore%20the%20said%20Writ%20Petitions%20for%20hearing%20before%20the%20High%20Court%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20apex%20court%20order%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESandeep%E2%80%99s%20SLP%20was%20filed%20through%20senior%20advocate%20Dushyant%20Dave%20and%20advocate%20Aparna%20Bhat.%20The%20petition%2C%20he%20says%2C%20was%20settled%20within%20just%20four%20hearings.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20it%20took%20over%20four%20years%20for%20these%20four%20hearings%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20pointing%20at%20the%20excruciatingly%20slow%20legal%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETaking%20the%20overall%20delay%20into%20account%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20observed%3A%20%E2%80%9CConsidering%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20controversy%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Writ%20Petitions%20were%20of%202019%20and%202016%20respectively%2C%20we%20are%20sure%20that%20the%20High%20Court%20will%20give%20necessary%20priority%20to%20the%20hearing%20of%20the%20Writ%20Petitions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20case%20background%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESatish%20Shetty%20was%20killed%20while%20he%20was%20in%20the%20process%20of%20investigating%20a%20land%20scam%20that%20allegedly%20involved%20IRB%20officials.%20On%20October%2015%2C%202009%2C%20he%20filed%20a%20cheating%20case%20at%20the%20Lonavala%20police%20station%20against%2013%20persons.%20Of%20them%2C%20two%20were%20IRB%20representatives.%20Shetty%20alleged%20that%20IRB%20representatives%20had%20used%20forged%20documents%20to%20deceitfully%20grab%20over%2085%20hectares%20of%20state-owned%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20Shetty%20continued%20his%20activism%2C%20he%20received%20threats%20to%20his%20life.%20He%20even%20had%20complained%20to%20the%20Lonavala%20police%20about%20this.%20The%20police%20failed%20to%20provide%20him%20with%20security%20and%20within%20days%2C%20he%20was%20stabbed%20to%20death%2C%20close%20to%20his%20house%20in%20Talegaon%20Dhabade.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20two%20closure%20reports%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20Satish%20Shetty%E2%80%99s%20death%2C%20Sandeep%20filed%20a%20case%20at%20the%20local%20police%20station%20naming%20Mhaiskar%20and%20a%20few%20other%20IRB%20representatives.%20However%2C%20only%20five%20persons%20%E2%80%93%20Vijay%20Dnayeshawar%20Dabhade%2C%20Pramod%20Dattatray%20Waghmare%2C%20Navnath%20Maruti%20Shelar%2C%20Dongra%20alias%20Dongarya%20Hanumanth%20Rathod%20and%20Shyam%20Ramchandra%20Dabhade%20%E2%80%93%20were%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20police%20filed%20a%20chargesheet%20against%20the%20five%20arrested%20persons.%20Sandeep%20had%20suspected%20a%20role%20of%20a%20larger%20network%20and%20eventually%20sought%20a%20CBI%20inquiry%20in%20the%20matter.%20The%20state%20transferred%20the%20case%20to%20the%20CBI%20in%20April%202010.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20Mhaiskar%2C%20an%20investigation%20was%20also%20sought%20against%20IRB%20lawyer%20Ajit%20Kulkarni%2C%20IRB%20liaison%20officer%20Jayant%20Dangre%20and%20former%20deputy%20superintendent%20of%20police%20Dilip%20Shinde.%20Both%20the%20local%20police%20and%20the%20CBI%20never%20proceeded%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20initial%20one%20year%2C%20the%20CBI%20dodged%20the%20matter%20and%20did%20not%20investigate%20the%20actual%20allegation%20made%20by%20Sandeep.%20It%20was%20only%20after%20the%20Bombay%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20scathing%20remarks%20that%20the%20CBI%20was%20compelled%20to%20conduct%20a%20proper%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Bombay%20high%20court%20had%20then%20observed%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CBefore%20concluding%2C%20it%20will%20be%20necessary%20to%20note%20down%20that%20for%20reasons%20best%20known%20to%20the%20local%20police%2C%20they%20never%20investigated%20the%20case%20from%20the%20angle%20of%20suspicion%20against%20Mhaiskar%2C%20the%20promoter%20of%20IRB%20infrastructure%E2%80%A6%20even%20though%20the%20name%20was%20specifically%20mentioned%20in%20the%20FIR%E2%80%A6%20After%20the%20investigation%20was%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20CBI%2C%20it%20was%20expected%20the%20CBI%20would%20investigate%20the%20case%20thoroughly%20from%20all%20the%20angles.%20But%20it%20appears%2C%20that%20for%20the%20last%20eight%20months%2C%20the%20CBI%20has%20not%20even%20touched%20any%20of%20the%20suspects%20of%20the%20murder%20for%20the%20reasons%20best%20known%20to%20the%20investigation%20officer.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6Maybe%20because%20all%20of%20those%20parties%20appear%20to%20be%20very%20powerful%20financially%20and%20otherwise.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20CBI%20case%2C%20the%20local%20Lonavala%20police%20was%20still%20handling%20the%20cheating%20and%20forgery%20case%20that%20Shetty%20had%20filed%20with%20them%20before%20he%20was%20murdered.%20At%20the%20end%20of%202011%2C%20the%20Lonavala%20police%20filed%20a%20%E2%80%9CC%20Summary%E2%80%9D%20case%20claiming%20that%20it%20was%20difficult%20to%20ascertain%20if%20the%20cheating%20and%20forgery%20had%20really%20taken%20place.%20The%20Wadgaon%20Maval%20magistrate%20court%20accepted%20this%20%E2%80%98closure%E2%80%99%20report%20on%20December%2027%2C%202011%20without%20any%20objection.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20rap%2C%20the%20CBI%20continued%20with%20the%20investigation.%20IRB%20Infra%20and%20its%20associate%20companies%20were%20raided%20by%20the%20agency.%20The%20CBI%20also%20moved%20the%20Bombay%20high%20court%20in%20appeal%20against%20the%20local%20police%E2%80%99s%20closure%20report%2C%20claiming%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20enough%20material%20available%20to%20chargesheet%20the%20accused%20persons%20and%20the%20filing%20of%20%E2%80%9CC%E2%80%9D%20summary%20was%20bad%20in%20law.%E2%80%9D%20The%20CBI%20asked%20that%20the%20land%20grab%20case%20be%20transferred%20to%20them%20as%20they%20had%20evidence%20that%20linked%20Shetty%E2%80%99s%20expos%C3%A9%20of%20the%20land-grabbing%20case%20to%20his%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20August%208%2C%202014%2C%20the%20land%20grab%20case%20too%20was%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20CBI.%20Strangely%2C%20within%20three%20days%2C%20the%20CBI%20filed%20a%20closure%20report%20in%20the%20murder%20case%20for%20%E2%80%9Clack%20of%20sufficient%20evidence%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20investigation%20was%20handled%20by%20one%20officer%20Sushil%20Pratap%20Singh.%20He%2C%20in%20the%20investigation%2C%20had%20identified%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmotive%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20was%20also%20able%20to%20unearth%20%E2%80%9Cevidence%20of%20abetment%2C%20bribes%20offered%2C%20and%20threats%20made%20to%20the%20deceased%E2%80%9D.%20In%20the%20update%20given%20to%20the%20high%20court%20then%2C%20he%20was%20able%20to%20attribute%20roles%20to%20each%20person%20named%20as%20accused%20in%20the%20FIR.%20Yet%2C%20in%20the%20most%20surprising%20and%20incomprehensible%20manner%2C%20the%20officer%20had%20later%20sought%20closure%20of%20the%20murder%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESingh%20had%20later%20called%20up%20Sandeep%20and%20said%20that%20the%20closure%20report%20was%20filed%20under%20tremendous%20pressure.%20Sandeep%20had%20recorded%20this%20conversation%20and%20in%202019%2C%20he%20had%20shared%20the%20recording%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fsatish-shetty-murder-roadblocks%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20sudden%20u-turn%20raised%20suspicion%20and%20the%20high%20court%20refused%20to%20accept%20the%20CBI%E2%80%99s%20findings.%20The%20court%20had%20compelled%20the%20CBI%20to%20go%20on%20with%20the%20investigation.%20For%20three%20years%2C%20the%20CBI%20continued.%20A%20few%20more%20places%20were%20%E2%80%9Craided%E2%80%9D%20and%20statements%20recorded.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20April%2013%2C%202018%2C%20however%2C%20the%20CBI%20appeared%20before%20a%20magistrate%20court%