n%20the%20face%20of%20an%20all-out%20Israeli%20invasion%20of%20Gaza%20would%20significantly%20set%20back%20an%20Iranian%20strategy%20for%20regional%20ascendancy%20pursued%20for%20over%20four%20decades%2C%20according%20to%20the%20people%2C%20who%20asked%20to%20remain%20anonymous%20due%20to%20the%20sensitivity%20of%20the%20discussions%20in%20Tehran.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYet%20any%20major%20attack%20against%20a%20US-backed%20Israel%20could%20exact%20a%20heavy%20toll%20on%20Iran%20and%20trigger%20public%20anger%20against%20the%20clerical%20rulers%20in%20a%20nation%20already%20mired%20in%20an%20economic%20crisis%2C%20said%20the%20officials%20who%20outlined%20the%20various%20military%2C%20diplomatic%20and%20domestic%20priorities%20being%20weighed%20by%20the%20establishment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThree%20security%20officials%20said%20a%20consensus%20had%20been%20reached%20among%20Iran's%20top%20decision%20makers%2C%20for%20now%3A%20Give%20their%20blessing%20for%20limited%20cross-border%20raids%20by%20its%20Lebanese%20proxy%20group%20Hezbollah%20on%20Israeli%20military%20targets%2C%20over%20200%20km%20away%20from%20Gaza%2C%20as%20well%20as%20low-level%20attacks%20on%20U.S.%20targets%20by%20other%20allied%20groups%20in%20the%20region.%20Prevent%20any%20major%20escalation%20that%20would%20draw%20Iran%20itself%20into%20the%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20in%20contact%20with%20our%20friends%20Hamas%2C%20Islamic%20Jihad%2C%20and%20Hezbollah%2C%26quot%3B%20Vahid%20Jalalzadeh%2C%20the%20head%20of%20parliament's%20National%20Security%20Committee%20said%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20according%20to%20Iranian%20state%20media.%20%26quot%3BTheir%20stance%20is%20that%20they%20do%20not%20expect%20us%20to%20carry%20out%20military%20operations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIran's%20foreign%20ministry%20didn't%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20about%20the%20country's%20response%20to%20the%20unfolding%20crisis%2C%20while%20Israeli%20military%20authorities%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20high-wire%20act%20for%20Tehran.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20loss%20of%20the%20power%20base%20established%20in%20the%20Palestinian%20enclave%20via%20Hamas%20and%20allied%20group%20Islamic%20Jihad%20over%20three%20decades%20would%20puncture%20those%20plans%2C%20which%20have%20seen%20Iran%20build%20up%20a%20network%20of%20armed%20proxy%20groups%20across%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20from%20Hezbollah%20in%20Lebanon%20to%20the%20Houthis%20in%20Yemen%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIranian%20inaction%20on%20the%20ground%20could%20be%20perceived%20as%20a%20sign%20of%20weakness%20by%20those%20proxy%20forces%2C%20which%20have%20been%20Tehran's%20principal%20weapon%20of%20influence%20in%20the%20region%20for%20decades%2C%20according%20to%20three%20officials.%20They%20said%20it%20could%20also%20dent%20the%20standing%20of%20Iran%2C%20which%20has%20long%20championed%20the%20Palestinian%20cause%20against%20Israel%2C%20a%20country%20it%20refuses%20to%20recognise%20and%20casts%20as%20an%20evil%20occupier.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Iranians%20are%20facing%20this%20dilemma%20of%20whether%20they%20are%20going%20to%20send%20Hezbollah%20to%20the%20fight%20in%20order%20to%20try%20to%20save%20their%20arm%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20or%20maybe%20they%20are%20going%20to%20let%20go%20of%20this%20arm%20and%20give%20it%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Avi%20Melamed%2C%20a%20former%20Israeli%20intelligence%20official%20and%20a%20negotiator%20during%20the%20first%20and%20second%20intifadas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20point%20where%20the%20Iranians%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BCalculating%20their%20risks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Survival%20Is%20Utmost%20Priority'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIran's%20strategic%20goals%20are%20countered%20by%20immediate%20military%20considerations%20as%20Israel%20-%20responding%20to%20Hamas'%20devastating%20attack%20on%20Oct.%207%20that%20killed%201%2C400%20Israelis%20-%20has%20unleashed%20an%20aerial%20blitz%20on%20Gaza%2C%20killing%20at%20least%204%2C300%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20-%20a%20major%20military%20power%20-%20is%20widely%20believed%20to%20have%20its%20own%20nuclear%20arsenal%2C%20though%20it%20will%20neither%20confirm%20nor%20deny%20this%2C%20and%20has%20the%20support%20of%20the%20United%20States%2C%20which%20has%20moved%20two%20aircraft%20carriers%20and%20fighter%20jets%20to%20the%20eastern%20Mediterranean%2C%20partly%20as%20a%20warning%20to%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20Iran's%20top%20leaders%2C%20especially%20the%20supreme%20leader%20(Ayatollah%20Ali%20Khamenei)%2C%20the%20utmost%20priority%20is%20the%20survival%20of%20the%20Islamic%20Republic%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20Iranian%20diplomat%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20why%20Iranian%20authorities%20have%20used%20strong%20rhetoric%20against%20Israel%20since%20the%20attack%20started%2C%20but%20they%20have%20refrained%20from%20direct%20military%20involvement%2C%20at%20least%20for%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20Oct.%207%2C%20Hezbollah%20has%20exchanged%20fire%20with%20Israeli%20forces%20along%20the%20Lebanese-Israeli%20frontier%20in%20clashes%20that%20have%20killed%2014%20of%20the%20Islamist%20group's%20fighters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETwo%20sources%20familiar%20with%20Hezbollah's%20thinking%20said%20the%20low-level%20violence%20was%20designed%20to%20keep%20Israeli%20forces%20busy%20but%20not%20open%20a%20major%20new%20front%2C%20with%20one%20characterising%20the%20tactic%20as%20waging%20%26quot%3Bsmall%20wars%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHezbollah%20leader%20Sayyed%20Hassan%20Nasrallah%2C%20who%20is%20known%20for%20issuing%20threats%20against%20Israel%20in%20speeches%2C%20has%20not%20given%20a%20public%20address%20since%20the%20crisis%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThree%20senior%20Israeli%20security%20sources%20and%20a%20Western%20security%20source%20told%20Reuters%20that%20Israel%20didn't%20want%20a%20direct%20confrontation%20with%20Tehran%20and%20that%20while%20the%20Iranians%20had%20trained%20and%20armed%20Hamas%2C%20there%20was%20no%20indication%20that%20they%20had%20prior%20knowledge%20of%20the%20Oct.%207%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKhamenei%2C%20the%20supreme%20leader%2C%20has%20denied%20Iran%20was%20involved%20in%20the%20attack%2C%20though%20he%20praised%20the%20damage%20inflicted%20on%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20and%20Western%20security%20sources%20said%20Israel%20would%20only%20attack%20Iran%20if%20it%20was%20directly%20attacked%20by%20Iranian%20forces%20from%20Iran%2C%20though%20cautioned%20that%20the%20situation%20was%20volatile%20and%20an%20assault%20on%20Israel%20from%20Hezbollah%20or%20Iranian%20proxies%20in%20Syria%20or%20Iraq%20that%20caused%20heavy%20casualties%20could%20change%20that%20calculus.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20miscalculation%20by%20Iran%20or%20one%20of%20its%20allied%20groups%20in%20gauging%20the%20scale%20of%20a%20proxy%20attack%20could%20change%20Israel's%20approach%2C%20one%20of%20the%20Israeli%20sources%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BNo%20US%20Boots%20On%20The%20Ground%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUS%20officials%20have%20made%20it%20clear%20their%20aim%20is%20to%20prevent%20the%20conflict%20from%20spreading%20and%20to%20deter%20others%20from%20attacking%20American%20interests%20while%20keeping%20Washington's%20options%20open.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20his%20way%20back%20from%20a%20visit%20to%20Israel%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20bluntly%20denied%20an%20Israeli%20media%20report%20saying%20that%20his%20aides%20had%20indicated%20to%20Israel%20that%20if%20Hezbollah%20initiated%20a%20war%2C%20the%20U.S.%20military%20would%20join%20the%20Israeli%20military%20in%20fighting%20the%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20true%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden%20told%20reporters%20during%20a%20refuelling%20stop%20at%20Germany's%20Ramstein%20Air%20Base%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3Eabout%20the%20Israeli%20report.%20%26quot%3BThat%20was%20never%20said.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhite%20House%20national%20security%20council%20spokesman%20John%20Kirby%20reiterated%20that%20Washington%20wanted%20to%20contain%20the%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20intention%20to%20put%20U.S.%20boots%20on%20the%20ground%20in%20combat%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters%20during%20the%20refuelling%20stop.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJon%20Alterman%2C%20a%20former%20State%20Department%20official%20who%20now%20heads%20the%20Middle%20East%20program%20at%20the%20CSIS%20think-tank%20in%20Washington%2C%20said%20Iranian%20leaders%20would%20feel%20pressure%20to%20show%20tangible%2C%20and%20not%20just%20rhetorical%2C%20support%20for%20Hamas%20but%20warned%20of%20the%20potential%20for%20events%20spinning%20out%20of%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20you%20get%20into%20this%20environment%2C%20things%20happen%20and%20there%20are%20consequences%20that%20nobody%20wanted%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverybody%20is%20on%20edge.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20crisis%20has%20also%20added%20to%20uncertainty%20in%20financial%20markets%20in%20America%20and%20beyond%2C%20boosting%20demand%20for%20%26quot%3Bsafe-haven%26quot%3B%20assets%20like%20gold%2C%20U.S.%20government%20bonds%20and%20the%20Swiss%20franc.%20The%20market%20reaction%20has%20so%20far%20been%20muted%2C%20though%20some%20investors%20warn%20that%20would%20change%20dramatically%20if%20the%20Gaza%20war%20escalated%20into%20a%20broader%20regional%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Neither%20Gaza%20Nor%20Lebanon'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20China-brokered%20reconciliation%20between%20regional%20rivals%20Iran%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia%20has%20further%20complicated%20matters%20for%20leaders%20in%20Tehran%20who%20want%20to%20avoid%20jeopardizing%20that%20%26quot%3Bfragile%20progress%26quot%3B%2C%20according%20to%20a%20former%20senior%20official%20who%20is%20close%20to%20top%20decision-makers%20in%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Iranian%20people%20themselves%20could%20play%20a%20role%20in%20events%20unfolding%20across%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIran's%20rulers%20can't%20afford%20a%20direct%20involvement%20in%20the%20conflict%20while%20struggling%20to%20quell%20mounting%20dissent%20at%20home%2C%20driven%20by%20economic%20woes%20and%20social%20restrictions%2C%20two%20separate%20officials%20said.%20The%20country's%20has%20seen%20months-long%20unrest%20triggered%20by%20the%20death%20in%20custody%20of%20a%20young%20woman%20last%20year%20and%20the%20state's%20persistent%20crackdown%20on%20dissent.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20economic%20woes%2C%20caused%20chiefly%20by%20crippling%20U.S.%20sanctions%20and%20mismanagement%2C%20have%20led%20many%20Iranians%20to%20criticize%20the%20decades-long%20policy%20of%20channelling%20funds%20to%20its%20proxies%20to%20expand%20the%20Islamic%20Republic's%20influence%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20slogan%20%26quot%3BNeither%20Gaza%20nor%20Lebanon%2C%20I%20sacrifice%20my%20life%20for%20Iran%26quot%3B%20has%20become%20a%20trademark%20chant%20in%20anti-government%20protests%20in%20Iran%20for%20years%2C%20underscoring%20the%20people's%20frustration%20with%20the%20establishment's%20allocation%20of%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIran's%20nuanced%20position%20emphasizes%20the%20delicate%20balance%20it%20must%20maintain%20between%20regional%20interests%20and%20internal%20stability%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20former%20senior%20Iranian%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697955960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fgpo0kb78_israel-tanks-on-gaza-border-reuters_625x300_22_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Firan-quandary-in-israel-ha