B%20PM%20Modi%20had%20said%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20peace%20summit%20in%20Egypt%2C%20UN%20chief%20Antonio%20Guterres%20urged%20a%20humanitarian%20ceasefire%20%26quot%3Bto%20end%20this%20godawful%20nightmare.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20negotiations%2C%20food%2C%20water%20and%20medicine%2C%20but%20no%20fuel%2C%20crossed%20from%20Egypt%20into%20Gaza%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20crossing%20closed%20afterwards%2C%20and%20UN%20officials%20said%20much%20more%20was%20needed.%20%26quot%3BGaza%20was%20a%20desperate%20humanitarian%20situation%20before%20the%20most%20recent%20hostilities%2C%26quot%3B%20five%20UN%20agencies%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20now%20catastrophic.%20The%20world%20must%20do%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697953980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fklid8dtk_aid-for-gaza-by-india_650x400_22_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisrael-hamas-war-india-sends-aid-for-war-torn-gaza-to-pass-through-egypts-rafah-border-4504063%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20today%20sent%20humanitarian%20aid%20to%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%20amid%20a%20war%20with%20Israel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisrael-hamas-war-india-sends-aid-for-war-torn-gaza-to-pass-through-egypts-rafah-border-4504063%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisrael-hamas-war-india-sends-aid-for-war-torn-gaza-to-pass-through-egypts-rafah-border-4504063%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisrael-hamas-war-india-sends-aid-for-war-torn-gaza-to-pass-through-egypts-rafah-border-4504063%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22M-cap%20of%2010%20valued%20firms%20plunge%20Rs%201.52%20trn%3B%20Reliance%2C%20TCS%20biggest%20laggar