%20in%20China's%20national%20security%20over%20the%20past%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpentagon-report-claims-china-now-has-over-500-operational-nuclear-warheads-4501609%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpentagon-report-claims-china-now-has-over-500-operational-nuclear-warheads-4501609%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpentagon-report-claims-china-now-has-over-500-operational-nuclear-warheads-4501609%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Roads%2C%20Airport%2C%20Helipads%3A%20Pentagon%20Report%20Flags%20China%20Infra%20Boost%20Near%20LAC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChina%20stepped%20up%20its%20military%20presence%20and%20infrastructure%20build-up%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20(LAC)%20in%202022%20amid%20the%20border%20tension%20with%20India%2C%20a%20Pentagon%20report%20has%20said.%20Underground%20storage%20facilities%2C%20new%20roads%2C%20a%20dual-purpose%20airport%20and%20multiple%20helipads%20are%20part%20of%20Beijing's%20infrastructure%20push%20along%20the%20LAC%2C%20according%20to%20'Military%20and%20Security%20Developments%20involving%20the%20People's%20Republic%20of%20China'%20report%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20early%20May%202020%2C%20sustained%20tensions%20along%20the%20India-China%20border%20have%20dominated%20the%20Western%20Theater%20Command's%20attention.%20Differing%20perceptions%20between%20India%20and%20the%20PRC%20regarding%20border%20demarcations%20along%20the%20LAC%2C%20combined%20with%20recent%20infrastructure%20construction%20on%20both%20sides%2C%20led%20to%20multiple%20clashes%2C%20an%20ongoing%20standoff%2C%20and%20military%20buildups%20along%20the%20shared%20border%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20adds%20that%20China's%20Western%20Theater%20Command%20implemented%20large-sca