%20in%20Gaza%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Natalie%20Sanandaji%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ENatalie%20Sanandaji%20is%20an%20American%20who%20attended%20the%20Tribe%20of%20Nova%20music%20festival%20on%20October%207.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20and%20her%20friends%20spent%20four%20hours%20running%20through%20the%20desert%20before%20they%20were%20rescued.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%2028-year-old%20said%20she%20learned%20later%20that%20she%20nearly%20missed%20being%20shot%20at.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Natalie%20Sanandaji%2C%20a%2028-year-old%20New%20York%20resident%20and%20%26quot%3BAmerican%20Jew%20born%20to%20Israeli%20and%20Iranian%20parents.%26quot%3B%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESanandaji%20originally%20went%20to%20Israel%20for%20a%20friend's%20wedding%20but%20was%20at%20the%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvideo-wreckage-destruction-at-israeli-festival-attacked-by-hamas-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ETribe%20of%20Nova%20musical%20festival%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3Eon%20October%207%20when%20a%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hrw.org%2Fnews%2F2023%2F10%2F18%2Fisrael%2Fpalestine-videos-hamas-led-attacks-verified%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHamas%20terror%20attack%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20resulted%20in%20the%20deaths%20of%20at%20least%20260%20concertgoers%20and%20employees.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20beginning%20of%20my%20trip%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20was%20going%20to%20be%20at%20the%20rave.%20I%20arrived%20with%20three%20other%20friends%20around%201%20a.m.%20We%20were%20there%20dancing%20for%20about%20two%20hours%20and%20around%203%20a.m.%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20take%20a%20break%20and%20sit%20at%20the%20campsite%20on%20the%20festival%20grounds%2C%20take%20a%20nap%2C%20and%20wake%20up%20for%20the%20sunrise%20set.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20woken%20up%20by%20one%20of%20the%20girls%20in%20our%20camp%2C%20who%20informed%20us%20that%20there%20had%20been%20some%20rockets%20that%20were%20sent%20our%20way%20and%20intercepted%20overhead.%20She%20just%20wanted%20us%20to%20be%20alert.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20other%20people%20would%20react%20the%20way%20that%20the%20festival%20attendees%20reacted.%20They%20were%20fairly%20calm.%20She%20reassured%20me%20that%20it%20would%20just%20probably%20be%20a%20few%20rockets%20and%20that%20this%20was%20a%20normal%20situation%20for%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20few%20minutes%2C%20the%20rockets%20kept%20coming.%20We%20started%20to%20realize%20that%20this%20wasn't%20just%20another%20normal%20situation.%20The%20festival%20security%2C%20at%20this%20point%2C%20had%20turned%20off%20the%20music%20and%20asked%20everybody%20to%20go%20straight%20to%20their%20vehicles.%20We%20picked%20up%20our%20things%20and%20went%20to%20our%20car.%20At%20this%20point%2C%20we%20thought%20that%20it%20was%20only%20rockets%20and%20that%20the%20worst%20danger%20that%20we%20could%20be%20in%20was%20that%20our%20car%20would%20get%20hit%20by%20some%20scraps%20from%20the%20rockets%20that%20were%20being%20intercepted%20by%20the%20Iron%20Dome.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEveryone%20was%20trying%20to%20leave%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20so%20we%20thought%20it%20would%20probably%20take%20a%20few%20extra%20hours%20to%20get%20home.%20So%20I%20asked%20my%20friends%20if%20they%20thought%20it%20was%20okay%20if%20I%20went%20back%20to%20the%20campgrounds%20to%20use%20the%20bathroom.%20I%20went%20back%20to%20use%20the%20bathroom%2C%20and%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20ago%20I%20saw%20a%20video%20that%20surfaced%20of%20the%20terrorists%20coming%20to%20those%20exact%20bathrooms%20and%20just%20shooting%20at%20the%20bathroom%20stalls%20trying%20to%20kill%20anybody%20who%20might%20have%20been%20inside.%20If%20I%20had%20been%20there%20moments%20later%2C%20that%20could%20have%20been%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20getting%20to%20our%20car%2C%20the%20festival%20security%20asked%20everybody%20to%20drive%20down%20in%20one%20direction%20on%20the%20dirt%20road.%20You%20couldn't%20drive%20on%20most%20of%20the%20open%20field%20and%20everybody%20was%20trying%20to%20get%20out%20at%20the%20same%20time%20on%20the%20same%20road.%20We%20started%20driving%20and%20the%20festival%20security%20started%20asking%20everyone%20to%20turn%20around%20and%20go%20in%20another%20direction.%20This%20was%20the%20second%20time%20where%20we%20started%20to%20really%20realize%20that%20something%20else%20was%20happening%20that%20we%20didn't%20fully%20know%20of%20yet.%20I'd%20also%20like%20to%20point%20out%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20security%20did%20their%20best%20to%20get%20everyone%20out%20safely%20and%20many%20of%20them%20died%20in%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20started%20going%20in%20the%20other%20direction.%20Suddenly%20security%20was%20asking%20everyone%20to%20please%20pull%20over%20on%20the%20side%20of%20the%20road%2C%20get%20out%20of%20their%20cars%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisraelis-palestinian-militants-invaded-fled-desert-festival-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estart%20running%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20for%20a%20second%2C%20we%20sat%20there%20and%20we%20didn't%20understand%20why%20they%20would%20say%20something%20like%20that.%20To%20us%2C%20the%20fastest%20way%20to%20get%20out%20of%20here%20was%20by%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20heard%20the%20first%20gunshots%2C%20that's%20when%20we%20realized%20that%20it%20wasn't%20just%20rockets%20and%20that%20the%20terrorists%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvideo-israel-hamas-gaza-paragliders-music-festival-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecome%20on%20foot%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20they%20had%20guns%2C%20and%20they%20were%20coming%20after%20us.%20As%20soon%20as%20we%20heard%20the%20gunshots%20we%20just%20opened%20our%20d