ct%2C%20where%20the%20concoction%20of%20geo-politics%20of%20emotions%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ereal%20politik%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20has%20furthered%20the%20diabolic%20interests%20of%20%E2%80%98atrocity%20propaganda.%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMarc%20Owen%20Jones%2C%20Associate%20Professor%20of%20Middle%20East%20Studies%20at%20Hamad%20bin%20Khalifa%20University%20at%20Doha%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fmarcowenjones%2Fstatus%2F1714196259584540804%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estated%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20five%20strategies%20of%20disinformation%20warfare.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20First%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20say%20something%20else.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ESecondly%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20ensure%20enough%20people%20use%20false%20information%20so%20that%20it%20becomes%20a%20%E2%80%98narrative.%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EThirdly%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20when%20it%20becomes%20a%20narrative%2C%20it%20then%20has%20to%20be%20%E2%80%98debunked%E2%80%99%2C%20unfairly%20putting%20burden%20of%20proof%20on%20journalists%2C%20etc.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EFourthly%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20debunking%20comes%20too%20late.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ELastly%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20the%20damage%20is%20done.%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20narrative%20put%20forward%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscholar.stjohns.edu%2Fcgi%2Fviewcontent.cgi%3Farticle%3D1104%26context%3Djovsa%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMinna%20Aslama%20Horowitz%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20an%20expert%20on%20digital%20rights%20and%20advocacy%2C%20Central%20European%20University%2C%20has%20explained%20how%20%E2%80%9Cdisinformation%20often%20through%20cyberwars%20and%20information%20disorder%20is%20manifested%20in%20many%20frontiers%20and%20for%20numerous%20reasons%2C%20including%20monetary%20gain%20and%20political%20power.%20An%20individual%E2%80%99s%20frustrations%20about%20social%20and%20economic%20conditions%20can%20turn%20into%20the%20fear%2C%20hatred%2C%20and%20vitriol%20that%20prompt%20simple%20acts%20of%20digital%20violence%2C%20such%20as%20creating%2C%20commenting%20on%2C%20and%20sharing%20rumors%2C%20falsehoods%2C%20and%20hate%20speech.%20Hence%2C%20information%20wars%20have%20many%20more%20soldiers%20than%20do%20cyberwars.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EScholars%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fprofile%2FCorneliu-Bjola%2Fpublication%2F346440120_Public_Diplomacy_in_the_Age_of_%2527Post-reality%2527%2Flinks%2F63f7f6f257495059453933ac%2FPublic-Diplomacy-in-the-Age-of-Post-reality.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIlan%20Manor%20and%20Corneliu%20Bjola%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20have%20explained%20that%20currently%20we%20are%20witnessing%20the%20age%20of%20%E2%80%98post%20reality%E2%80%99%20which%20is%20characterised%20by%20states%20fracturing%2C%20contesting%20and%20assaulting%20reality.%20The%20driving%20force%20behind%20%E2%80%98post-reality%E2%80%99%20is%20digitalisation%20through%20which%20states%20create%20a%20world%20of%20competing%20realities%20which%20erode%20social%20cohesion%2C%20amplify%20social%20tensions%2C%20drive%20social%20frustration%20and%20prevent%20individuals%20from%20making%20sense%20of%20the%20world%20around%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%2C%20now%20that%20we%20are%20tightly%20incarcerated%20in%20the%20world%20of%20falsehoods%2C%20propaganda%2C%20deep-fakes%2C%20sock-puppets%20and%20voice%20clones%2C%20how%20do%20we%20understand%20what%20is%20true%3F%20The%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict%20has%20become%20a%20mouthpiece%20for%20Islamophobia%20and%20further%20causing%20divisions%20between%20Judaism%20and%20Islam.%20Martyrdom%20and%20political%20violence%2C%20cloaked%20by%20religious%20propaganda%20has%20added%20fuel%20to%20this%20%E2%80%98post-reality%E2%80%99%20we%20live%20in%20%E2%80%93%20an%20apocalyptic%20nightmare%20where%20human%20lives%20are%20rendered%20meaningless%20in%20invisible%20ignominy%20and%20hatred.%20The%20debates%20on%20asymmetrical%20balance%20of%20power%20and%20the%20apartheid%20occupation%20of%20Israel%20through%20illegal%20settlements%20are%20being%20replaced%20by%20the%20politics%20of%20deception%2C%20denial%20and%20distortion.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20I%20write%20this%2C%20the%20world%20has%20forgotten%20that%20on%20December%207%2C%202022%2C%20an%20Israeli%20Zionist%20soldier%20Yosed%20Diamont%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fincontextmedia%2Fstatus%2F1600493875746963457%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20an%20interview%20to%20Israeli%20Channel%20Hot%208%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20openly%20confessed%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20put%20Palestinians%20in%20cages%20and%20killed%20them.%20One%20of%20us%20raped%20a%2016-year-old%20girl%3B%20some%20of%20us%20ran%20after%20them%20with%20flame%20throwers%20and%20burned%20them.%E2%80%9D%20Or%20that%20as%20of%20today%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Freliefweb.int%2Freport%2Foccupied-palestinian-territory%2Fisrael-destroys-quarter-northern-gaza-strip-palestinian-death-toll-exceeds-4000-enar%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAccording%2520to%2520documentation%2520by%2520Euro%2Cthem%2520being%2520children%2520and%2520women.%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edeath%20toll%20in%20Gaza%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20risen%20to%204%2C079%20with%20more%20than%2015%2C000%20wounded.%20And%20this%20is%20just%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20end.%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EDr.%20Shubhda%20Chaudhary%20is%20a%20West%20Asia%20political%20analyst%20and%20editor%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20India%20West%20Asia%20Dialogue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697942139000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%