3E%3Cli%3EKinzinger%20in%20the%20past%20has%20been%20a%20vocal%20critic%20of%20ousted%20Speaker%20Kevin%20McCarthy%20of%20California.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20ex-congressman%20said%20that%20he%20was%20unsure%20if%20the%20House%20GOP%20could%20govern%20going%20forward%2C%20given%20its%20slim%20majority.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20Rep.%20Adam%20Kinzinger%20has%20a%20tough%20message%20for%20his%20former%20colleagues%20now%20struggling%20to%20select%20a%20replacement%20for%20ousted%20ex-House%20Speaker%20Kevin%20McCarthy%3A%20buckle%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjnPiCbY-ZWw%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDuring%20a%20Friday%20appearance%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20PBS%20NewsHour%20journalist%20Geoff%20Bennett%20in%20conjunction%20with%20Politics%20and%20Prose%20bookstore%2C%20Kinzinger%20was%20asked%20if%20House%20Republicans%20had%20the%20capacity%20to%20govern%20as%20a%20majority%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20response%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20they%20had%20maybe%20a%2040%2C%2050-vote%20majority%2C%20yeah%2C%20you%20can%20always%20minimize%20the%20bomb-throwers%20or%20the%20minority%20of%20a%20viewpoint%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Illinois%20Republican%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20in%20this%20current%20setup%20if%20they%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHouse%20Republicans%20now%20have%20a%20narrow%20221-212%20majority%2C%20and%20over%20two%20weeks%20after%20McCarthy's%20ouster%2C%20neither%20Reps.%20Jim%20Jordan%20of%20Ohio%20nor%20Steve%20Scalise%20of%20Louisiana%20were%20able%20to%20amass%20the%20217%20votes%20needed%20to%20secure%20the%20speakership.%20So%20the%20selection%20process%20for%20a%20new%20leader%20goes%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20as%20Kinzinger%20noted%20in%20his%20interview%2C%20the%20United%20States%20faces%20a%20series%20of%20crises%20%E2%80%94%20both%20domestic%20and%20abroad%20%E2%80%94%20which%20require%20the%20full%20attention%20of%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20we'll%20be%20lucky%20as%20a%20country%20to%20get%20through%20a%20government%20shutdown%20without%20having%20to%20shut%20it%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20congressman%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe'll%20be%20lucky%20as%20a%20country%20to%20get%20Israel%20and%20Ukraine%20aid%20on%20the%20floor%20and%20done.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUltimately%2C%20I%20think%20they%20will%20be%20able%20to%20govern%20to%20get%20those%20things%20done%20because%20the%20pressure%20will%20be%20too%20high%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued%2C%20referencing%20House%20Republicans.%20%26quot%3BBut%20in%20terms%20of%20pushing%20any%20Republican%20agenda%20per%20se%2C%20or%20really%20doing%20anything%20proactively%20for%20the%20country%2C%20no%2C%20I%20think%20the%20party%20is%20going%20to%20be%20in%20survival%20mode%20and%20frankly%20get%20its%20backside%20rightfully%20handed%20to%20it%20in%20the%20next%20election.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKinzinger%20was%20elected%20to%20the%20House%20in%20the%20Tea%20Party%20wave%20of%202010%2C%20which%20brought%20a%20legion%20of%20conservatives%20looking%20to%20reform%20government.%20However%2C%20over%20a%20decade%20later%2C%20he%20emerged%20as%20a%20fierce%20critic%20of%20both%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20McCarthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Republicans%20narrowly%20took%20the%20House%20majority%20last%20fall%2C%20Kinzinger%20%E2%80%94%20who%20was%20a%20prominent%20member%20of%20the%20House%20January%206%20committee%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkinzinger-house-republicans-nonfunctional-majority-mccarthy-freedom-caucus-democrats-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epredicted%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20party%20would%20have%20a%20%26quot%3Btotally%20nonfunctional%20majority%26quot%3B%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20Kinzinger%20also%20blasted%20McCarthy%20for%20what%20he%20said%20was%20the%20California%20Republican's%20capitulation%20to%20th