ory%2Famp%2Fisrael-gaza-latest-idf-increases-strikes-as-hamas-says-it-attempted-to-release-two-more-hostages-12989656%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22An%20orca%20species%20that%20helped%20humans%20hunt%20whales%20for%20thousands%20of%20years%20may%20now%20be%20extinct%2C%20new%20research%20reveals%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20orca%20swimming.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65105751e2c0220019ef31b1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221631%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThaua%20hunters%20sang%20to%20orcas%20as%20they%20hunted%20whales%20side-by-side%20for%20thousands%20of%20years.%3Cp%3EEnrique%20Marcarian%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAn%20orca%20species%20that%20hunted%20alongside%20humans%20for%20thousands%20of%20years%20is%20likely%20locally%20extinct.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20finding%20is%20thanks%20to%20DNA%20analysis%20of%20a%20100-year-old%20skeleton%20and%20knowledge%20from%20the%C2%A0Thaua%20people.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOrcas%20swam%20alongside%20Thaua%20hunters%20and%20led%20them%20to%20whales%20for%20thousands%20of%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20thousands%20of%20years%2C%20the%20Thaua%20people%20%E2%80%94%20members%20of%20the%20Yuin%20nation%20in%20eastern%20Australia%20%E2%80%94%20had%20an%20exceptional%20whale%20hunting%20strategy%2C%20a%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Facademic.oup.com%2Fjhered%2Fadvance-article%2Fdoi%2F10.1093%2Fjhered%2Fesad058%2F7308443%3Flogin%3Dfalse%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20peer-reviewed%20Journal%20of%20Heredity%20described.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThaua%20hunters%20learned%20that%20they%20could%20work%20together%20with%20orcas%20in%20Australia's%20Twofold%20Bay%2C%20helping%20lead%20them%20straight%20to%20their%20prey.%20Some%20Thaua%20hunters%20even%20sang%20to%20the%20orcas%20to%20encourage%20them%20to%20herd%20whales%20inland.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20hunters%20killed%20the%20whales%2C%20the%20orcas%20would%20eat%20only%20the%20lips%20and%20tongue%2C%20while%20the%20hunters%20would%20take%20the%20rest%2C%20Steven%20Holmes%2C%20a%20Thaua%20Traditional%20Custodian%20and%20coauthor%20of%20the%20study%2C%20wrote.%20The%20practice%20was%20called%20the%20%26quot%3BLaw%20of%20the%20Tongue%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20Holmes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20relationship%20lasted%20for%20generations%20until%20the%201930s%20%E2%80%94%20about%20150%20years%20after%20British%20colonizers%20arrived%20in%20Australia%20%E2%80%94%20when%20the%20orcas%20vanished%20from%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20long%20unclear%20what%20happened%20to%20the%20orcas.%20But%20thanks%20to%20DNA%20analysis%20of%20a%2023-foot-long%20orca%20skeleton%20from%20almost%20100%20years%20ago%20and%20knowledge%20from%20the%20Thaua%20people%2C%20scientists%20now%20believe%20the%20species%20is%20locally%20extinct.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsabella%20Reeves%2C%20a%20doctoral%20student%20who%20led%20the%20study%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livescience.com%2Fanimals%2Forcas-that-hunted-alongside-humans-might-be-extinct%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELive%20Science%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it's%20unclear%20exactly%20how%20the%20relationship%20between%20the%20Thaua%20whalers%20and%20orcas%20first%20began%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it%20likely%20existed%20for%20thousands%20of%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20what%20I've%20learned%20from%20killer%20whales%20is%20that%20they're%20curious%2C%20they%20can%20be%20strategic%2C%20and%20when%20they%20want%20something%2C%20they%20know%20how%20to%20get%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Reeves%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20skeleton%20Reeves%20studied%20was%20named%20Old%20Tom.%20He%20had%20served%20as%20a%20hunting%20companion%20all%20the%20way%20until%20his%20death%2C%20Holmes%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20people%20had%20a%20long-lasting%20friendship%20with%20the%20beowa%20in%20Eden%2C%20especially%20Old%20Tom%2C%26quot%3B%20Holmes%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BMy%20Nan%2C%20Catherine%20Holmes%20nee%20Brierly%2C%20told%20us%20about%20her%20great%20Grandfather%2C%20Budginbro%2C%20who%20along%20with%20other%20Thaua%2C%20would%20swim%20with%20Old%20Tom%2C%20holding%20on%20to%20his%20dorsal%20fin.%20My%20ancestors%20were%20never%20hurt%20or%20injured.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Forca-that-hunted-alongside-humans-extinct-australia-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697916299000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653420a1be9edfa8eda6da36%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Forca-that-hunted-alongside-humans-extinct-australia-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20thousands%20of%20years%2C%20Thaua%20hunters%20in%20eastern%20Australia%20hunted%20whales%20with%20the%20help%20of%20orcas.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22khawkinson%40insider.com%20(Katie%20Hawkinson%20)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A176%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Forca-that-hunted-alongside-humans-extinct-australia-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Will%20the%20Monster%20Success%20of%20%E2%80%98Taylor%20Swift%3A%20The%20Eras%20Tour%E2%80%99%20Bring%20Back%20the%20Concert%20Film%3F%20It%20Should%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697913651000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2FGettyImages-1484033557-e1684074898794.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235763966%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hollywood%20loves%20to%20repeat%20success%2C%20and%20now%20more%20than%20ever%20it%20needs%20to.%20If%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20promising%20way%20to%20draw%20people%20into%20movie%20theaters%20that%20the%20industry%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20