20Additionally%2C%20Corbett%20is%20the%20best%20example%20of%20nature%20at%20its%20best.%20I%20have%20been%20to%20many%20other%20national%20parks%20too%2C%20but%20I%20always%20found%20Corbett%20more%20beautiful%20than%20any%20place%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20few%20visits%2C%20he%20found%20a%20five-acre%20land%20in%20a%20small%20village%20called%20Bhatoli%20in%20the%20Corbett%20area.%20Sunando%20decided%20to%20build%20an%20eco-friendly%20home.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20place%20was%20in%20bad%20shape%20when%20we%20bought%20it.%20The%20trees%20and%20wildlife%20near%20it%20were%20mostly%20destroyed.%20So%20we%20started%20with%20planting%20500%20trees%20and%20making%20the%20place%20green%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20adding%20that%20over%20the%20years%2C%20he%20has%20planted%20more%20than%205%2C000%20trees%20on%20the%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20house%20is%20done%20using%20locally%20sourced%20stones%20and%20%3Cem%3Emitti%20%3C%2Fem%3E(mud)%20from%20the%20area.%20We%20wanted%20to%20support%20the%20local%20communities%20around%20the%20area%3B%20hence%2C%20we%20only%20employed%20people%20from%20the%20villages%20to%20help%20us%20construct%20the%20homestay%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20adding%20that%20all%20materials%20were%20locally%20sourced%2C%20and%20the%20homestay%20solely%20hires%20local%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAdditionally%2C%2095%20percent%20of%20the%20homestay%20is%20running%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F173892%2Fbengaluru-sustainable-home-solar-power-rainwater-harvesting-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eon%20solar%20energy.%3C%2Fa%3E%20There%20are%20only%20a%20few%20things%20that%20require%20electricity.%20We%20also%20do%20rainwater%20harvesting%20and%20have%20a%20storage%20capacity%20of%201%2C00%2C000%20litres%20of%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captio