n%20visiting%20the%20place%20with%20his%20family%20for%20more%20than%20five%20years%20now%2C%20shares%20what%20it%20feels%20like%20to%20stay%20at%20Tanhau.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20place%20is%20surreal%20and%20I%20am%20not%20exaggerating%20when%20I%20say%20that%20it%20is%20the%20best%20experience%20I%20have%20ever%20had.%20It%20is%20so%20peaceful%20and%20quiet%3B%20it%20teaches%20you%20the%20importance%20of%20slow%20living.%20The%20best%20part%20is%20that%20it%20is%20a%20very%20sustainable%20setup.%20It%20feels%20good%20to%20know%20that%20I%20am%20travelling%20and%20not%20leaving%20a%20carbon%20footprint%20behind.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20teach%20my%20son%20the%20importance%20of%20preserving%20nature%20and%20this%20homestay%20was%20the%20perfect%20place%20to%20do%20so.%20We%20participated%20in%20the%20project%20with%20a%20school%20near%20the%20homestay%20where%20we%20tried%20to%20spread%20awareness%20about%20the%20harmful%20effects%20of%20plastic%20and%20its%20carbon%20footprint%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20bid%20to%20promote%20slow%20and%20responsible%20travel%2C%20the%20homestay%20hosts%20unique%20activities%20to%20engage%20the%20guests.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20walking%20safaris%20in%20the%20buffer%20forest%2C%20which%20is%20an%20amazing%20and%20unique%20experience%20in%20itself.%20Of%20course%2C%20you%20can%20take%20a%20safari%20and%20sit%20in%20a%20jeep%2C%20but%20on%20a%20walking%20safari%2C%20you%20can%20observe%20nature%20and%20animals%20closely%2C%20without%20emitting%20any%20carbon.%20We%20also%20organise%20village%20walks%20and%20encourage%20our%20guests%20to%20participate%20in%20any%20ongoing%20village%20festivals%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20guest%2C%20Avika%20Sood%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20silence%20in%20the%20place%20is%20rejuvenating.%20I%20found%20out%20about%20the%20homestay%20through%20a%20friend%20and%20have%20visited%20it%20a%20few%20times.%20The%20place%20is%20offbeat%20and%20unique.%20There%20is%20so%20much%20to%20learn%20about%20the%20wildlife%20and%20animal%20kingdom%2C%20and%20Sunando%20is%20a%20walking%20library%20in%20that%20sense.%20He%20is%20very%20passionate%20about%20his%20work.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Ftanhau-1-1-1697812365.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tanhau%20has%20hosted%20over%20500%20guests%20at%20their%20mud%20homestay.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Ftanhau-1-1-1697812365.jpg%20840w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Ftanhau-1-1-1697812365-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Ftanhau-1-1-1697812365-500x261.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Ftanhau-1-1-1697812365-768x401.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Ftanhau-1-1-1697812365-150x78.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332764%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22439%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETanhau%20has%20hosted%20over%20500%20guests%20at%20their%20mud%20homestay.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Tanhau%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9COne%20thing%20that%20I%20found%20very%20refreshing%20about%20the%20hosts%20is%20that%20they%20have%20ensured%20that%20they%20give%20more%20to%20nature%20than%20they%20take%20from%20it.%20Since%20I%20have%20been%20visiting%20them%20year%20after%20year%2C%20I%20have%20seen%20the%20place%20grow%20into%20a%20green%20oasis.%20Every%20time%20I%20visit%2C%20there%20is%20a%20new%20sustainable%20addition%20to%20the%20place.%20Like%20initially%20when%20I%20visited%2C%20they%20did%20not%20have%20rainwater%20harvesting%2C%20but%20now%20they%20harvest%20several%20litres%20of%20rainwater.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%20on%20his%20journey%20so%20far%2C%20Sunando%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWith%20my%20experience%2C%20I%20could%20have%20been%20a%20CEO%2C%20but%20that%20life%20was%20not%20for%20me.%20I%20prefer%20living%20close%20to%20nature%20and%20advocating%20sustainability.%20I%20am%20not%20sure%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20my%20work%20with%20the%20villagers%20and%20at%20the%20homestay%2C%20but%20I%20still%20want%20to%20try%20to%20leave%20a%20legacy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat)%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697813127000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D332749%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Weary%20of%20living%20in%20cities%2C%20Sunando%20Sen%20sold%20his%20startup%2C%20packed%20his%20bags%20and%20bought%20land%20in%20Corbett.%20There%2C%20he%20constructed%20a%20sustainable%20home%20called%20%E2%80%98Tanhau%E2%80%99%20after%20restoring%20the%20land%20with%20trees.%20Here's%20a%20look%20at%20his%20journey%20of%20moving%20towards%20a%20sustainable%20lifestyle.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332749%2Fex-banker-sunando-sen-built-tanhau-sustainable-himalayan-homestay-corbett-restore-wildlife%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%226%20Indian%20Scientists%20Who%20Were%20Nominated%20for%20The%20Nobel%20Prize%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20the%20life%20and%20legacy%20of%20six%20brilliant%20Indian%20scientists%20who%20were%20nominated%20for%20the%20prestigious%20Nobel%20Prize%20throughout%20the%20years%20%E2%80%93%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20Thiruvengadam%20Rajendram%20Seshadri%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-